query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.role, u.tipoUsuarioId, tu.nome as tipoUsuarioNome 
FROM user u 
LEFT JOIN tipo_usuario tu ON u.tipoUsuarioId = tu.id 
WHERE u.email = 'cirocouceiro@me.com'
